overview: Comedy, Stand-Up - Watch some of the best country comedians -- including Cousin Minnie Pearl, Jerry Clower, Roger Miller, The Statler Brothers and Jeff Foxworthy -- as they yuk it up in this collection of side-splitting stand-up routines from the past and present. The laughs were amassed by the legendary Jim Owens, producer of some of the biggest hits in country music.
title: Classic Country Comedy
